data.description: POOL HOME WITH OVER 3,000 SQFT in an established community with lake access to the  Clermont Chain of Lakes. Ready to move in now! This community offers private access to the NEW pickleball/tennis/  basketball courts, and more. This home has an incredibly flexible floor plan that will  satisfy the needs of any homeowner! HUGE master bedroom suite with an attached  14x12 room nestled behind French doors that make this private area an amazing home office/  nursery/workout room,or a sanctuary to curl up with a good book and relax with a cup of  coffee or evening beverage. Dual walk-in closets lead you into the master bathroom w/dual  vanities, soaking garden tub, and separate OVERSIZED glassed-in shower. The HUGE family  room has 18-foot ceilings, which make this room appear even larger. Both walls can  accommodate a massive flatscreen TV! As the family room is also open to the kitchen area, it is  easy to stay connected with everyone while cooking and watching TV. The kitchen has beautiful  granite countertops including a center island, so serving many guests is easy. Stainless steel appliances including a newer French door refrigerator, recessed lights, tons of cabinets and storage room, plus pretty tiled backsplash make this an  amazing space. Host BBQs, holiday meals, or large gatherings with ease by utilizing the HUGE  formal dining room, or the large breakfast nook that leads to the covered lanai. With the casual  dining area being large enough for a table that seats 6 or 8, you may want to utilize the formal  dining or living room or both for home offices, homeschool rooms, or even transform one into a  4th bedroom. These rooms have double-tray ceilings, and the way they were both designed,  would be quite simple to finish off 2 half walls and add a door. All the rooms in this home are VERY LARGE compared to any new  home construction, including the 2nd and 3rd bedroom, both have large walk-in closets, and one  has the views out of the back of the home of the backyard and pool. The rear lanai is covered  and has a screened patio and pool area that’s expertly framed with mature landscaping that  offers just enough privacy. An irrigation well supplies the in-ground sprinkler system so that  water bills stay under $15 a month! The laundry room has a laundry sink and tons of cabinets  which leads you into the side entry of the oversized 2 car garage. The driveway is extra-long for  additional parking space. New roof 2020, 2 Newer AC units installed in 2018, Newer updates to  include flooring in most rooms and BRAND-NEW carpeting in ALL bedrooms. This is a  meticulously maintained home, ready to move in, and a quick move in is possible. Come enjoy  all this home, community and area has to offer. Nearby are waterfront multi-purpose and bike trails, or take advantage of the private community boat ramp and launch your boat on Lake Minneola, part of  the Clermont Chain of Lakes and go wakeboarding, waterskiing, fishing, or take a casual tour  through the dozen or so lakes. Stop by the Tiki Bar just around the corner, stop by the newly  revitalized downtown Clermont area and the proposed up and coming city boat dock to tie up  to and go shop, eat, or visit a brewery downtown or even one of the many events or farmers  markets! Lake Minnehaha has a marina with bar/food trucks and live music on the weekends.  Lake Louisa has a state park and a great place to see lots of nature. Come see this AMAZING  home after watching the interior/drone video!
